msgstr "前提条件"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/nixl.rst:17
msgid "**LMCache**: Install with ``pip install lmcache``"
msgstr "**LMCache**: 使用 ``pip install lmcache`` 安装"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/nixl.rst:18
msgid ""
"**NIXL**: Install from `NIXL GitHub repository <https://github.com/ai-"
